data.description: Now is your chance to own a pool home in the fabulous area of Johns Lake Estates.  This large family home is located on a quiet cul de sac in a well-kept community.  No need to worry about the roof or the AC both are new!  Love to entertain? Invite your guests into your private wet bar right off of your grand living area. There are 4 bedrooms upstairs and the 2-car garage has been professionally enclosed for a large 5th bedroom or office space. The garage is not included in the listed square footage. The Seller is willing to convert it back if needed. Open kitchen, with an island and faux-finished cabinets. The large master bedroom, and nice size extra bedrooms make this the perfect family home. For boat and lake lovers, there is a private community boat launch to John's Lake.
